  "title": "Shuttle Bus Driver (12 Seaters)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a leading provider of maritime energy solutions.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Shuttle Operator (Toyota Hiace)</li>\n  <li>Safely drive the company-owned shuttle bus (12-14 passenger capacity) according to assigned schedules and locations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely arrivals for picking up staff and adherence to the allocated driving schedule.</li>\n  <li>Keep the bus fuelled, well-maintained, safe, and presentable at all times while ensuring compliance with passenger limits.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a valid Class 3 driving license</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of experience <strong>driving a Toyota Hiace or comparable vehicles with a capacity of 12-14 passengers</strong>.</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with Singapore routes and a consistent record of safe and clean driving.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
